					<div class="blog">
	<h1>
		Accommodation	</h1>
	
	



	<div class="category-desc">
				<p><img src="/images/stories/accommodation/accommodation.png" border="0" alt="Accommodation" title="Accommodation at the Club" /><br /><br />The top floor of the University Club offers accommodation in 14 en-suite guest rooms, consisting of 2 single rooms, 10 double rooms and 2 twin rooms.  One twin room and one double room are equipped for disabled guests and there is a double room which has an inter-connecting door to one of the single rooms, ideal for carers or as a family room.  All the rooms have a hospitality tray, TV, telephone and WIFI, iron and ironing boards are available on request. The accommodation rooms have excellent views across the Club&#39;s playing field towards Marston.  <br /><br />Please book online or call reception to check availability.</p>		<div class="clr"></div>
	</div>


<div class="items-leading">
			<div class="leading-0">
			
	<h2>
					<a href="/accommodation/39-room-tariffs">
			Room Tariffs</a>
			</h2>





<hr id="null" />
<p>Rates quoted are up to the 31st of December 2014 and is subject to change without notice.<br />Breakfast and VAT included, accommodation payable in full at time of booking</p>
<table style="width: 424px; height: 84px;" border="1" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Single</td>
<td>Non Members: £78.00</td>
<td>Members: £73.00</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Double/twin</td>
<td>Non Members: £98.00</td>
<td>Members: £93.00</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Family Room</td>
<td>Non Members: £153.00</td>
<td>Members: £148.00</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Extra Bed</td>
<td>Non Members: £40.00</td>
<td>Members: £36.00</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><strong>Check in time 1400               Check out time 1000<br /><br /></strong>Please contact reception for any enquiries on 01865 271044 or email <a href="mailto:reception@club.ox.ac.uk">reception@club.ox.ac.uk</a> <br /><br />Members ID is required at check in for the discounted rates<br /><br />Internal departments: please email reception to make a reservation <a href="mailto:reception@club.ox.ac.uk">reception@club.ox.ac.uk</a> or call 71044</p><div class="attachmentsContainer">

