			<div class="items-row cols-1 row-0">
		<div class="item column-1">
		
	<h2>
					<a href="/accommodation/37-booking">
			Room Booking</a>
			</h2>





<hr id="null" />
<p><strong>PLEASE NOTE THAT WE OFTEN HAVE PARTIES ON WEEKEND WITH MUSIC. IF THIS IS OF AN INCONVENIENCE PLEASE CALL RECEPTION TO CHECK PARTY DATES.</strong></p>
<p><strong>Book online using the booking system</strong> : <a href="https://roomres.club.ox.ac.uk/" target="_parent" title="Room booking">https://roomres.club.ox.ac.uk/</a></p>
<p>(please note this will take you to a third party website) If you have any problems please contact reception.</p>
<p>OR <strong>Book direct </strong>at <a href="mailto:reception@club.ox.ac.uk">reception@club.ox.ac.uk</a> Tel: +44 (0)1865 271044</p>
<p>All payments are required in advance at time of booking.</p>
<p>(Please note that reception is manned 0800 - 1600 Monday to Friday, outside of these times the duty manager will endeavour to answer queries)</p>
<p>For Directions please see our <a href="/contact-a-information">About Us section</a></p>
<p>When booking please include  any club membership details (preferably the University card number)</p>
<ul>
<li>Telephone: +44 (0)1865 271044</li>
<li>Web booking: <a href="https://roomres.club.ox.ac.uk/" target="_parent" title="Room booking">https://roomres.club.ox.ac.uk/</a></li>
</ul>
<p>The Club does not have allocated parking space, apart from limited bays for drivers with a disabled ( blue ) badge.</p>
<p>For car parking on Mansfield road, please see the attachment.</p><div class="attachmentsContainer">

