						<div class="items-row cols-1 row-1">
		<div class="item column-1">
		
	<h2>
					<a href="/accommodation/38-room-facilities">
			Room Facilities</a>
			</h2>





<hr id="null" />
<p>All Rooms Offer the following facilities:</p>
<ul>
<li>ensuite shower room</li>
<li>tea/coffee making facilities</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>telephone</li>
<li>internet connection and WIFI</li>
<li>hair dryer</li>
</ul>
<p>Iron and ironing board available at reception on request<br /><br />There are 2 rooms fully equipped for disabled users, and one with an adjoining room for a carer.</p><div class="attachmentsContainer">

<div class="attachmentsList" id="attachmentsList_com_content_default_38"></div>

</div>


<div class="item-separator"></div>
	</div>
						<span class="row-separator"></span>
				</div>

						<div class="items-row cols-1 row-2">
		<div class="item column-1">
		
	<h2>
					<a href="/accommodation/41-cancellation-charges">
			Cancellation Policy</a>
			</h2>





<p style="text-align: justify;">Payment is required in full at the time of booking.  If a cancellation is received in writing more than 7 days before the day of arrival, no cancellation fee is charged and a full refund is given. If the booking is cancelled less than 7 days in advance, you will be refunded 50% of the room charge. 100% of the  fee will be charged if the cancellation is not received before 9am the day before the day of arrival,  or is a "no show". ANY CHANGES TO RESERVATIONS MUST BE MADE IN WRITING.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Policy for multiple room bookings and long term stay bookings (any number of rooms booked for 4 nights or longer):</strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #333333; line-height: 115%; font-family: ">Payment is required in full at the time of booking. If a cancellation is received in writing more than 30 days before the date of arrival, no cancellation fee is charged and a full refund is given. If the booking is cancelled more than 15 days in advance, you will be refunded 50% of the charge. 100% of the fee will be charged if the cancellation is not received by 9am 15 days before the day of arrival, or is a "no show". ANY CHANGES TO RESERVATIONS MUST BE MADE IN WRITING.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"> </p><div class="attachmentsContainer">

